{"tid":317195,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"楊潤雄：副學士是「獨立有價值資歷」　","createTime":"2017-07-11T09:35:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-11T10:51:09.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a21378ee9fdde9ff79ae2cba3f921eb9d56d7bfa","tid":317195,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T09:35:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170711/s00001/e7b5255ea27391b9fad5544002fdea1d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170711%2Fs00001%2Fe7b5255ea27391b9fad5544002fdea1d.jpg&h=c34c2b56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中學文憑試（DSE）明日放榜。問到今年考生人數下跌，學位會否供過於求，以及會否藉此取消副學士等，教育局長楊潤雄強調副學士是「獨立而有價值資歷」，舉例指有副學士憑這有關資歷在政府工作等等，形容成效「有一定作用」，但由於面對很多不同意見，故是時候檢討。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，檢討副學士不是因為供求問題，而是因應社會對副學士的意見，「是時候檢討」，重申與「報考人數」及「可能入學人數」無關係。<br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄又呼籲文憑試考生放鬆心情，指政府提供很多升學就業途徑，而若遇到問題，要與朋友、家長、老師商量，「希望大家都有好成績」。<br />\n<br />\n至於特首林鄭月娥今早出席行政會議前，率先宣布延續「三保政策」兩年，即剩餘教師可申請保留教席多兩年，楊潤雄稱此舉是要令教育團隊安心。"},{"pid":"ace081ab2c73d60cfc4a7cd902ee907c8813a0ff","tid":317195,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T09:35:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170711/s00001/1499760557335\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170711%2Fs00001%2F1499760557335&d=lov1Do8XFtxWa9%2BicBDhuL5jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=5f3ed1d4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170711%2Fs00001%2F1499760557335&h=1139ce8e\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170711/s00001/1499760557335</a>"},{"pid":"78b519a2a2f9d989b4ff6aea300a98fbb1a1c8cb","tid":317195,"uid":183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T09:50:50.000Z","msg":"比d垃圾上大學<br />\n<br />\n都有用既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p